- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper proposes a modification to the Batch Normalization algorithm, which is commonly used in machine learning for neural network training. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing): The paper focuses on improving the convergence of neural network training, which falls under the scope of this sub-category. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition): The paper tests the proposed algorithm on complex modern CNN models, which are commonly used in computer vision tasks. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes a modification to a commonly used algorithm in artificial intelligence (AI) and tests it on various datasets. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): Although not the primary focus of the paper, the convergence analysis of the proposed algorithm involves analyzing the behavior of different parameters, which could fall under the scope of this sub-category.
